As a consulting firm, Alithya undertakes a wide variety of technically challenging and interesting projects, and so your exact responsibilities will vary depending on the project to which you are assigned. Our clients are typically from technology department with large firms, and each project is typically 6 months to 2 years in duration. In between project assignments, you will work in our Toronto office, assisting with managing our internal new products and solutions. You will be reporting to the VP of Financial Sector and be working with both client and/or Alithya employees to provide project management services providing trustworthy consulting work. We are looking to hire full time and on a permanent basis.


